// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1862 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f34c3a62-a429-5851-ba2d-9a31ede386a0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
